We have a lot of projects that have date based information in them (HR management, finance/estimates, hosting management etc)

While we have made some dashboards showing useful information, however there's a lot of scenarios where the users want to be able to select date ranges on a dashboard that then adjust the information the dashboard shows based on start/end date pickers

This would require support in both the JQL side (to indicate what fields mapped to what parts of the select query) and the dashboard itself (would need a widget to actually select the date). There's pieces of user documentation around about how to achieve similar things, but it all seems very hacky and I feel that this type of feature would be a huge benefit to the product suite

